The exponax project is itself inspired by the spinX module of
Chebfun and cites the following works for numerical methods:

  - Cox, S. M., & Matthews, P. C. (2002). Exponential time
    differencing for stiff systems. Journal of Computational
    Physics, 176(2), 430–455.
  - Kassam, A.-K., & Trefethen, L. N. (2005). Fourth-order
    time-stepping for stiff PDEs. SIAM Journal on Scientific
    Computing, 26(4), 1214–1233.
